targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__unixEpochGroupAlias(time_measured,$__interval),
  temperature AS "Temperature [°C]",
  humidity AS "Humidity [g/m³]",
  relative_humidity AS "Relative Humidity [%H]"
FROM measurements
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter(time_measured)
ORDER BY $__unixEpochGroup(time_measured,$__interval)

panels.content: Press ESC to change the selected time span in the upper right-hand corner.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  time_measured AS "time",
  station_id
FROM measurements
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time_measured)
ORDER BY time_measured

FROM measurements
